@startuml
title Full Delivery E2E Golden Path

actor Board
participant "Squadrail API" as API
participant "Engineer" as ENG
participant "Reviewer" as REV
participant "Tech Lead" as TL
database "Isolated Worktree" as WT

Board -> API: Create company / project / workspace
Board -> API: Create tech lead / engineer / reviewer
Board -> API: Create issue
Board -> API: ASSIGN_TASK

API -> ENG: assignment wake
ENG -> API: ACK_ASSIGNMENT
ENG -> API: START_IMPLEMENTATION
API -> ENG: implementation follow-up wake
ENG -> WT: edit code + run test/build
ENG -> API: SUBMIT_FOR_REVIEW

API -> REV: review wake
REV -> API: START_REVIEW
REV -> API: APPROVE_IMPLEMENTATION

API -> TL: approval wake
TL -> API: CLOSE_TASK

API -> Board: issue done + artifacts + run history

note right of WT
  Success requires:
  - isolated workspace used
  - actual diff exists
  - tests/build pass in worktree
end note

@enduml
